race.comment: SWEET LOLLIPOP (4) jumped from box 1 last time and ran away with an impressive win scoring by 5 lengths at this track in a handy 23.56. Has the squeeze box to overcome and will need the breaks early. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Great chance to get the job done again. EDGEWOOD (2) boasts a strong record this journey here with 14 wins and 11 minors from 32 tries. In the money last time at this track (24.05) in a OPEN, finishing a 4.5 lengths third. Can feature with the right run. BAREFOOT ROGUE (1) was below best at her last start when 8th at this track following a win (23.86) there two back. Has a good record here at this journey. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. PAW ALLEY (8) has won at this course and distance â€“ one to keep very safe.
